                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Reserve.
            </p>
            <p class="identDIV">
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Em outra panela, aque&ccedil;a o azeite e refogue o alho com o gengibre.
            </p>
